Hehe 🤩 So grateful to see lots of SG kiddos enjoy our Felt magnets Printable Materials!! 😍😍 They are so cute!!
.

Free printable materials such as matching magnets and colouring pages can be downloaded and printed in the comfort of your own homes 🥳 ** It’s under magnet section on TOKI website and available to download upon check out ✨
.
Hope these materials are useful and injects fun and laughter during your #WFH and #HBL #schoolholidays ❤️
.

Enjoy extended fun & engaging activities with our Best-selling Felt Magnets! Please note that these materials are for personal use only and prohibited from any type of commercial use.
.

4 more weeks to go! We can go through this time together 👍🏻👍🏻
.
